      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Segment: Insert</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Insert Segment</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">Use </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Insert-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> to add a new segment immediately to the left of the </text><text styleclass="Element-Header" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Notes"><text styleclass="Notes" translate="true">Note: </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">The </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Width2" styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Motion-Width</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> increases by </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">90º </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">(or an equivalent value for other X-axis </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" anchor="Motion" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">units</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">If you want to add a new segment, but you do </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">NOT</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> want to increase the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Motion-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">, it is better to use </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-InsertBP-At" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">Insert Blend-Point at</link><text styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> or </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-InsertBP-Mouse" styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">Insert-Blend-Point</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">.</text></para>
